summary:
IT’S THE 2ND ANNIVERSARY OF LIE SHORT FILM!!

When these WINGS Short Films came out on 2016, I was so mesmerized by BTS’s acting...
caption:
IT’S THE 2ND ANNIVERSARY OF LIE SHORT FILM!!

When these WINGS Short Films came out on 2016, I was so mesmerized by BTS’s acting skills. They’ve always been good actors, but the individual short films showed the extent of their abilities. It was this LIE short film I think that made me a great Jimin bias. He was so amazing and on point with the background music, and the CINEMATOGRAPHY OMG I LOVE IT SO MUCH 😍😍😍That bathtub water scene at the end! It gave me so much goosebumps! 😍

NOTE: These short films are based on Demian novel, classic literature. WINGS album was based on this novel. The songs were also written & inspired by this novel as well as intertwining BU (Bangtan/BTS Universe) & possibly BTS’s personal experiences. WINGS remains one of the most iconic BTS eras and shows the depth of BTS’s musical artistry through intellectual/philosophical music. Demian became a bestselling novel in South Korea because of BTS when WINGS came out, just like other books they’ve recommended/referenced up to today~

body:
I know this was supposed to be a cute love story mv or whatever and maybe im just overthinking but I hate how some parts of this are parallel to some details of the recently released notes when will bighit let us live 😭

1. Hoseok working at a restaurant

2. Namjoon working at a gas station

3. Taehyung in a convenience store where he met the girl

4. All of them hanging out in a room/storage area

5. Yellow lollipop

The only lie in this was jk not asking yoongi out on a date lmao
